name: compiler_deep_v8_array_index_after_mutated_index
section: runtime-arrays-v8
args: p:Bool a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Mutable index variable should affect the later array-as-function lookup.
law: (= (with [xs [{a} {b}] i 0] (do (when {p} (set! i 1)) (xs i))) (if {p} {b} {a}))
